\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid148921 After the Kathisma, the Symbol of Faith)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid148921 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid148921 \sect }\sectd \ltrsect\psz1\linex0\endnhere\titlepg\sectlinegrid360\sectdefaultcl\sftnbj \pard\plain \ltrpar
\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid4022315 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 After the Kathisma, the Symbol of Faith:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 
\par 
\par I believe in one God, the Father Almighty, Maker of heaven and earth, and of all things visible and invisible. 
\par 
\par And in one Lord Jesus Christ. the Son of God, the Only-begotten, begotten of the Father before all ag
es. Light of Light; true God of true God, begotten, not made; of one essence with the Father by Whom all things were made; Who for us men, and for our salvation, came down from the heavens,  and was incarnate of the Holy Spirit and the Virgin Mary, and be
c
ame man; And was crucified for us under Pontius Pilate, and suffered, and was buried; And arose again on the third day according to the Scriptures; And ascended into the heavens, and sitteth at the right hand of the Father. And shall come again, with glor
y, to judge both the living and the dead; Whose kingdom shall have no end. 
\par 
\par And in the Holy Spirit, the Lord, the Giver of Life; Who proceedeth from the Father; Who with the Father and the Son together is worshipped and glorified; Who spake by the prophets. 
\par 
\par In One, Holy, Catholic, and Apostolic Church. I confess one baptism for the remission of sins. I look for the resurrection of the dead, And the life of the age to come. Amen.
\par 
\par Then:
\par 
\par Holy God, Holy Mighty, Holy Immortal, have mercy on us}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 . (Thrice)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 
\par 
\par Glory to the Father, and to the Son, and to the Holy Spirit, both now and ever, and unto the unto the ages of ages. Amen.
\par 
\par O Most Holy Trinity, have mercy on us. O Lord, blot out our sins. O Master, pardon our iniquities. O Holy One, visit and heal our infirmities for Thy name's sake. 
\par 
\par Lord have mercy. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 (Thrice)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181  
\par 
\par Glory to the Father and to the Son and to the holy Spirit, both now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. Amen. 
\par 
\par Our Father, Who art in the Heavens, hallowed by Thy Name. Thy K
ingdom come, Thy will be done, on earth as it is in Heaven. Give us this day our daily bread. And forgive us our debts, as we forgive our debtors. And lead us not into temptation, but deliver us from the evil one. Amen. 
\par  
\par PRIEST:  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs24\b\f1\fs36\insrsid6177181 For Thine is the Kingdom and the power and the glory, of the Father, and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs28\i\f1\insrsid6177181 READER: }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181  Amen. 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 
