\par Then:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181  Lord, have mercy. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 Forty times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 And this Prayer of the Hours:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 
\par 
\par Thou Who at all times and every hour, in heaven and in earth, art worshipped and glorified, O Christ God, Who art long-suffering, plenteous in mercy, most compassionate, Who loveth the righteous and hast mercy on sinners, Who callest al
l to salvation through the promise of good things to come: Receive, O Lord, our prayers at this hour, and guide our life toward Thy commandments. Sanctify our souls, make chaste our bodies, correct our thoughts, purify our intentions, and deliver us from 
every sorrow, evil and pain. Compass us about with Thy holy angels, that, guarded and guided by their array, we may attain to the unity of the faith and the knowledge of Thine unapproachable glory; for blessed art Thou unto the ages of ages. Amen. 
\par 
\par Lord have mercy. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 Thrice
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 
\par Glory to the Father, and to the Son, and to the Holy Spirit, both now and ever, and unto the unto the ages of ages. Amen.
\par 
\par More honorable than the Cherubim, and beyond compare more glorious than the Seraphim, who without corruption gavest birth to God the Word, the very Theotokos, thee do we magnify.
\par 
\par In the name of the Lord, father }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 (Master) }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 bless. 
\par 
\par PRIEST: }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs24\b\f1\fs36\insrsid6177181 God be gracious unto us and bless us, and cause Thy face to shine upon us, and have mercy on us. 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs28\i\f1\insrsid6177181 READER: }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid6177181  Amen 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 \sect }\sectd \ltrsect\psz1\linex0\endnhere\titlepg\sectlinegrid360\sectdefaultcl\sftnbj \pard\plain \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \rtlch\fcs1 
\af0\afs24\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs29\i\f1\cf6\insrsid6177181 
